Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:13.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是  课题的小论文么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,能够参加的只有七个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:21.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,每天都在努力学习和收集情报  一定没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:28.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,对星星和宇宙的回忆么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:34.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,与蓝相遇  变得想要更加了解星星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:37.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,加入地学部  学习了石头的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,还体会到了把星星的知识传递给大家的快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:43.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:46.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,烧烤？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:51.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我想让一年级的两位新生留下各种开心的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:55.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,所以就像去年那样一起来烧烤如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:57.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,说不定是个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:59.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也和猪猪学姐和远藤老师商量下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:04.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,早已经安排上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:06.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不愧是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:11.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这周周末，将举行新生欢迎烧烤会。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:13.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,有想吃的东西记得告诉我哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:15.09,Asteroid - HandWrite3,,0,0,0,,{\frx358\fry348\frz346.2\pos(1504,600.333)}请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:14.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:17.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,吃着美味的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.32,0:08:20.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在河边收集石头  观察月亮和星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:22.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真是一群悠哉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:24.77,Asteroid - Chat,,0,0,0,,{\move(927.8,1090.267,927.8,882.6,300,0)pos(934.467,882.6)}我想要做烤棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:28.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,说不定是个可爱的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:36.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,白棉花糖  黄棉花糖  粉棉花糖
Comment: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:36.66,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,/软棉花糖  内含胶原蛋白
Comment: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:36.66,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,/柠檬棉花糖  柔软  轻飘飘
Comment: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:36.66,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,/草莓棉花糖  内含果冻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:38.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就像绕口令一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:41.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈  果然棉花糖买多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:44.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我想让七海同学高兴下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:47.08,Asteroid - Chat,,0,0,0,,{\frz14.35\pos(958.933,581.756)\3c&HECB17C&}星星棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:46.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那一袋是给自己用的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:49.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,接下来就是食材的准备呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:53.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是的  久违的烧烤真令人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:09:00.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,天气预报明明说是多云…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:02.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是不是延期举办比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:05.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是食材也已经买了一大堆了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:07.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,改地点了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:08.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我来车站接你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:09.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,铃也叫上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:11.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:12.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不愧是烧烤执行官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:13.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,待会见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:19.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:22.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这样的话下雨也没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,早上一醒来就是这样的天气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:29.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也不想改日子  赶紧调查了下雨也能举行的场地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:32.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,铃同学  今年也谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:34.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没事没事  不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:37.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就是这样  之后就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,烤好肉了再叫醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:45.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,新学期最初的活动就下雨…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:47.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:50.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我带来了很多纸巾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:52.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:55.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,太可爱了  猪猪学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:58.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,多做几个一定能放晴的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:09:59.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,大家一起做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:04.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,比起这个  继续做烧烤的准备不是更好么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:06.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,跟从姐姐那儿听到的悠闲度完全一致
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:24.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,大家都很熟练呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:26.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,去年和前年都做过的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:29.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,话说  这个互动总觉得很怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:34.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,如果在河边的话  收集石头和天体观测都可以进行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.47,0:10:36.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但这样下去哪样都没办法做了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  小七  小千
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:40.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小千？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:41.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小七？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:45.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这样顺其自然地取外号的感觉也很怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:48.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.47,0:10:51.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:54.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:02.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,肉真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:04.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,确实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:06.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,在外面吃更是别有一番风味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:07.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,虽然这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:11.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,感觉雨变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:15.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是大概一两个小时就会停吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:18.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,难道说小七可以预测天气么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:21.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我的话也可以用鞋子占卜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:26.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:28.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我只是看了看手机上的天气预报
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:30.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,话说这样会弄脏鞋子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:35.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,太美味了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:41.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,七海同学想要做的气象学科  也包含了天气预报的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:42.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:45.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,只要与天气相关的不管什么都有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.57,0:11:47.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,风  云  大气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:48.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,以及关于灾害也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:52.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那个  总觉得提到这个的时候你有些不开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.82,0:11:55.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,让亲戚留下了不好的回忆  所以这是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:11:59.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,其实在三年前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:02.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,亲戚家里遭受了洪水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:05.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,幸好没有人受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:09.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但我已经不想再看到阿姨露出那样的神情了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.30,0:12:11.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,想必很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:15.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,所以我必须要成为能够帮助别人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:24.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,七海同学  这个送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.10,0:12:26.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是蓝玛瑙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:28.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,和式名字叫做空色缟玛瑙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:32.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,可以帮助你平心静气  平缓身心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:36.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,还是不要太勉强自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:39.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也没有勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:42.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你在做什么  占卜？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:44.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你眉头上起皱纹了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:48.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,总之  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:52.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,气象学对七海同学来说就像是身边的东西一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:55.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,像是运用在天气预报和防灾上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:13:00.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,比起天文学地质学更贴近生活  更有作用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:01.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那天文学也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:05.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,观测小型天体和陨石碎片是否会撞到地球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:08.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,还有发射各种人造卫星等等  都发挥了作用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.17,0:13:10.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,地质学也在我们的身边发挥了作用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:11.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,比如…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:14.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,突然想不出例子来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:17.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,对于预测地震和勘探矿产资源
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:19.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,以及挖采油田都起到了作用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:22.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,甚至石头能够指引人们通往幸福的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:26.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,最后的不属于地质学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:26.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不属于呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:36.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,照片  录像带  手信都全沾满了泥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:38.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,阿姨…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:41.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我讨厌雨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:44.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,还有那污浊的泥水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.27,0:13:47.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,和一无是用的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:50.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我仅仅是在做自己该做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:55.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,雨终于停了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.37,0:13:57.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不枉我们做了这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:13:59.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:01.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,快看小七  出彩红了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:05.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是环地平弧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:07.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,环地平？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:12.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,并不是彩虹  而是一种名为环地平弧的大气光学现象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:16.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,六角形的冰粒经由光线的折射所以看上去就像是彩虹的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:18.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是十分罕见的现象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:22.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我其实也是第一次看到实物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:31.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:33.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,对了  拍下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:34.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:36.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我想刊登在会刊上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.62,0:14:38.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,七海真是博识呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:39.42,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,米菈 蓝 过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:40.37,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:42.00,Asteroid - UP,,0,0,0,,那拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:43.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,因为我有目标  这是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:49.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,为了帮助别人而学习  我觉得这是很厉害的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:57.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,只是也希望七海能够意识到并珍视它  自己其实也乐在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:15:00.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,眉间的皱纹消了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:04.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不快点拍的话就要消失了  七海同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:08.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,既然都给我取了昵称了  就叫我七七吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:11.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那么我们拍吧  小七
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:16.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,大伙  年轮蛋糕烤好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:17.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,年轮蛋糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:21.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:22.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:25.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:29.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这个地层很不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:31.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,弯弯的  看上去像是褶曲地层
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:35.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,baum是树的意思吧  怎么会是树龄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:37.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小七真是不解风情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.07,0:15:42.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你们高兴就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:45.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,话说回来  这些瘆人的棉花糖是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:48.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,咦  我不记得我有买过这种颜色的棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:51.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小七  你烤糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:01.20,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,太开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:04.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我还得去准备明天用的材料  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:06.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好的  今天真是多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:11.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这个天气要是早点出现就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:12.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:15.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我们再稍微坚持一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:21.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,像遇见这样天气好的日子  我们就会练习使用望远镜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:22.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,请看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:26.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,月亮好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:29.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,对吧  旁边的是木星哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:32.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这要多少倍镜才能看见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:34.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:37.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,镜筒的焦距是910毫米
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:39.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,目镜是15毫米  所以是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:44.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这个透镜的话大概是60倍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:47.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,对的  调整一下角度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:49.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,拍好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:53.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没想到手机也能拍出这样的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.52,0:16:55.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这叫做对镜拍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:59.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,如果不习惯的话会很难  没想到七海同学这么擅长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:01.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,叫我七七就行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:07.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,说起来  你们两个的小论文的进展怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:08.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小论文？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:14.88,Asteroid - HandWrite4,,0,0,0,,{\fs90\frz84.49\pos(582.4,655.6)}KIRA星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:14.88,Asteroid - HandWrite4 - up,,0,0,0,,{\fs90\frz84.49\pos(582.4,655.6)}KIRA星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:14.88,Asteroid - HandWrite4,,0,0,0,,{\fs100\frz80.18\c&HD77AD7&\pos(1150.4,506.8)}挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:14.88,Asteroid - HandWrite4 - up,,0,0,0,,{\fs100\frz80.18\c&HD77AD7&\pos(1150.4,506.8)}挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:11.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,Kira星挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:15.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小论文就像是参加这个的考试一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:16.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,虽然还没有完成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.10,0:17:19.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是每天晚上都在一起做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:20.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,每天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:23.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,晚上出门  你们是不良吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:29.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,蓝学姐  她们两人为了实现一起寻找小行星的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:33.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,和家人分开居住在米菈学姐家里对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:34.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,听姐姐这么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:37.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,和家人分开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:41.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,如此毅然决然  想必很不容易吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:43.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,什么  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:44.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:50.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:52.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,泥土占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:54.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也叫地相术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:58.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,稍微想占卜一下学姐她们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:00.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:02.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:05.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是只要行动就能前行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:11.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不会吧  真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.61,Asteroid - Mail,,0,0,0,,发出人：国立天文台
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.61,Asteroid - Mail,,0,0,0,,收件人：木之幡米菈\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.61,Asteroid - Mail,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}书面选拔考试通过通知
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.61,Asteroid - Mail,,0,0,0,,\N木之幡米菈     同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.61,Asteroid - Mail,,0,0,0,,\N我是国立天文台的广濑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.61,Asteroid - Mail,,0,0,0,,感谢您能够参加本次Kira星挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.61,Asteroid - Mail,,0,0,0,,根据书面选拔的结果    木之幡米菈您的申请被采用    祝贺您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.61,Asteroid - Mail,,0,0,0,,\N为确认您的参加意愿    请再准备好飞机票后与往返日期行程后\N回复我们（台风时的运行状况也请确认一下）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.61,Asteroid - Mail,,0,0,0,,\N往返石垣的飞机票和参加Kira星挑战前一天以及结束后的住宿\N（必要的情况）请根据自身的情况安排
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.61,Asteroid - Mail,,0,0,0,,关于在石垣岛的交通方式    请从石垣岛飞机场乘坐公交到石垣\N岛宾馆（如果需要购买物品的话请在离岛终点站或者是公交终\N点站等市中心下车）之后乘坐的士比较便利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.61,Asteroid - Mail,,0,0,0,,如果是居住在石垣岛的青少年    请在离机场最近的公交站点下\N车便是石垣岛宾馆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.61,Asteroid - Mail,,0,0,0,,如果是去往石垣岛的青少年的话    请不要携带者行李在盛夏的\N石垣岛中徒步行走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:14.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,太好了  蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:16.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我通过了书面考试
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:17.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那真是可喜可贺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:21.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,实在是可喜可贺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:24.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这条新闻就将成为我们新闻部的头条
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:26.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就让我刊登在报道上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:29.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,本来是想去实地追踪报道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:31.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,可是由于经费问题无法实现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:39.97,Asteroid - HandWrite6,,0,0,0,,{\c&H454578&\pos(1000,1074.429)}金楚糕               石垣岛盐           八重山荞麦面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:33.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,作为补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:36.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我整理了石垣岛的特产资料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:39.97,Asteroid - HandWrite3,,0,0,0,,{\frz4.064\c&H454578&\fs70\pos(1022.858,688.143)}在石垣岛要买东西的话就买这些!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:39.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就拿去做手信的参考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:44.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,学姐真是的  太兴奋了还有太鲁莽了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:46.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:49.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我没有通过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:54.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:57.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,看上去两人好像丢了魂一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:19:01.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,只有一个人通过  千景的占卜真是太准了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:03.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:06.95,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但是你们要振作起来  还有其它的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:09.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,学姐  你这根本就不算是鼓励
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:11.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,学姐们…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:14.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈  蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:15.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎么无精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:17.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,你们好  好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:20.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,樱学姐还有梦露学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:24.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,学姐  你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:29.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,果然有学姐们在我就觉得好安心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:32.30,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,从千景那里听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:34.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好不容易才挤过了独木桥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:36.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,哪来的时间给你浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:37.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.75,0:19:40.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,虽然只有一个人能去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.52,0:19:42.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但得到的知识是能共享的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:46.12,Asteroid - Chat,,0,0,0,,{\pos(884.572,202.428)\3c&H8796A8&\3a&HFF&}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.47,0:19:46.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,之后要是还有什么问题就找我们商量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:48.62,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好的  谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:50.17,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:54.27,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不好  忘了恭喜米菈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:57.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小樱你还是没有变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:04.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,虽然深感孤独  但将会有着新的变局产生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:08.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,丢掉旧的价值观  相信自己的直觉前进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:11.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,这是占卜学姐们后得到的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:13.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,希望能够帮助到学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:19.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好像说是远藤老师陪着我去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:21.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那我就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:22.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.67,0:20:25.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要是一个人去冲绳的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:28.70,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我…肯定…会迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.00,0:20:29.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:33.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我好想和你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:36.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.95,0:20:38.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,一点都不像平时的你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:41.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,正如大家所说的  我们必须得向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:43.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:47.45,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我也会想一想有没有我能为你做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:51.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,感觉蓝突然变得很可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:07.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,那我们出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:08.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.85,0:21:10.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,很期待你的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:12.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,还有礼物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:21.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,没想到连我们也有一些感伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.15,0:21:25.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但也不过是几天而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.77,0:21:28.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我会每天给你打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:33.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:37.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,接下来  先借个车
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:37.97,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:43.40,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,蓝？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:46.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我…我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:50.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.65,0:21:53.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.62,0:21:56.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎么一回事
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,——————ED——————
